# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2.2.7] - 2025-11-10

### Added

- Now the whole `FirestoreDAO` implements the `Logger` to allow an easy debug.

## [2.2.5] - 2025-11-10

### Added

- Implemented `Logger` in `create`.

## [2.2.4] - 2025-11-10

### Added

- Implemented `Logger` in `countBy`.

## [2.2.3] - 2025-11-10

### Added

- Implemented `Logger` in `search`.

## [2.2.2] - 2025-11-09

### Added

- Implemented `Logger` in `getAll`.

## [2.2.1] - 2025-11-09

### Added

- Added `Logger` as optional consutrctor dependency of the `FirestoreDAO`.
- Implemented `Logger` in `findByID`.
- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [2.1.6] - 2025-11-09

### Changed

- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [2.1.5] - 2025-11-08

### Changed

- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [2.1.4] - 2025-11-08

### Changed

- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [2.1.3] - 2025-11-07

### Changed

- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [2.1.2] - 2025-11-02

### Added

- Added support for private fields. Now the private attribute will be ignored and the getter will be used.

## [2.1.1] - 2025-11-02

### Fixed

- Introduce the existance validation on `create` to the transaction if uow is present.

## [2.1.0] - 2025-11-02

### Added

- Added `FirestoreUnitOfWorkRunner`.

## [2.0.1] - 2025-11-01

### Fixed

- Added export of `FirestoreTransactionUnitOfWork` to entry point.

## [2.0.0] - 2025-11-01

### Added

- Added `FirestoreTransactionUnitOfWork`.

### Changed

- Renamed `FirestoreUnitOfWork` to `FirestoreBatchUnitOfWork`.
- Updated Shared Kernel.

## [1.2.7] - 2025-10-30

### Added

- Added validation on `create` method. Now a `DocAlreadyExists` exception is raised if a doc with the
provided id already exists.

## [1.2.6] - 2025-10-24

### Fixed

- Restored missing changes due to github missing push. Missing changes caused that `findOneBy` and `search` methods didn't apply correctly the criteria.

## [1.2.1] - 2025-10-14

### Added

- Added support for `DateValue` on in the `PrimitiveTypesToFirestoreFormatter`.

## [1.2.0] - 2025-10-14

### Added

- Added `countBy` method to the `FirestoreDAO`.

### Changed

- Updated `@schorts/shared-kernel` to `2.6.0`.
